# tri

A task management CLI app written in Go, using [cobra](https://github.com/spf13/cobra) framework.
Based on [this guide](https://spf13.com/presentation/building-an-awesome-cli-app-in-go-oscon/)


## Init go mod

```bash
go mod init github.com/natifridman/tri
```

## Get cobra

```bash
go get -u github.com/spf13/cobra@latest
```

## Initialize Cobra app

```bash
cobra-cli init . -a "Nati Fridman"
```

## Build the app

```bash
go build
./tri
```

## Add command

```bash
cobra-cli add add
./tri add
```

## Usage
```bash
Usage:
  tri [command]

Available Commands:
  add         Add a new todo
  completion  Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell
  done        Mark Item as Done
  help        Help about any command
  list        List the todos

Flags:
      --datafile string   data file to store todos (default "/Users/nafridma/Documents/projects/tri/.tridos.json")
  -h, --help              help for tri
  -t, --toggle            Help message for toggle

Use "tri [command] --help" for more information about a command.
```